      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom-quality condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it was first delivered. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish without a single swirl mark or stone chip. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the leather still smelling fresh and showing zero signs of wear or creasing. Every mechanical component has been serviced to the highest standard, and all electronics function perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously preserved example that has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and driven only on clear days.",
